%%{init: {'theme': 'dark'}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Running: Agent/Workflow Starts
    Running --> EvaluateRisk: After MCP + Generation
    EvaluateRisk --> PendingReview: Medium/High Risk OR Missing Info OR Low Confidence
    EvaluateRisk --> Completed: Low Risk + High Confidence + No Blockers
    
    PendingReview --> Approved: Human Approves
    PendingReview --> Rejected: Human Rejects
    PendingReview --> NeedsRevision: Human Requests Changes
    
    Approved --> Completed
    NeedsRevision --> Running: Agent Re-runs with Feedback
    Rejected --> Terminated
    
    Completed --> [*]
    Terminated --> [*]
    
    note right of PendingReview
      Human Review Task created
      in DB with full context snapshot.
      Workflow is checkpointed.
    end note
